Package ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.widgets.views

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CleanableWidget
    Cleanable Widget This interface makes the widget implementing it cleanable.
    ContainableWidget
    Containable Widget This interface makes the widget implementing it containable.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CAN
    CAN This class represents the content of a CAN message as received from the server.
    DataDisplayer
    Data Displayer This class is in charge of displaying a set of CAN messages in a legible way.
    DisplayLogWidget
    Display Log Widget This class is a log console type of widget responsible of stacking every CAN message the client is receiving (if no list of CAN messages provided) or stacking received CAN messages only if they figure in the list of CAN messages to display.
    FindMe
    Find Me This class is responsible of displaying a 3D arrow that is pointing towards the rocket considering its GPS position.
    MapTag
    Map Tag Displays map using osmdroid
    ModuleStatus
    Module Status Displays the module status in a grid layout.
    OronosView
    Oronos View Each view that displays data coming from an Oronos rocket extends Oronos View.
    Plot
    Plot The Plot class is a View that displays a single plot.
    UnsupportedWidget
    Unsupported Widget This class is for any xml type not covered by the scope of this project.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CAN.DisplayState
    Enum that is all the possible display states a CAN message can have.
    DataDisplayer.DataLayout
    This enum represents every possible layout the Data Displayer can have.
